---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="MarketMate Case Study">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to case studies</a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-1">Building MarketMate</h1>
    <div class="text-[12px] text-gray-500 mb-3">Case Study • 2024-2025</div>
    <p class="text-gray-600 md:w-3/4 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.9">How I built a food subscription platform that connects local farmers with consumers in Ghana.</p>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">The Problem</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          I noticed that people in Ghana were struggling to get fresh, local produce consistently. 
          Farmers had great food but limited reach, and consumers wanted fresh vegetables but didn't know where to find them.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          The existing solutions were either too expensive, didn't focus on local farmers, or were too complicated for everyday use.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">The Solution</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          I decided to build a subscription-based platform that would:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Connect local farmers directly with consumers</li>
          <li>Offer weekly curated boxes of fresh produce</li>
          <li>Allow customers to swap items they don't want</li>
          <li>Provide pickup points in convenient locations</li>
          <li>Share stories about the farmers and their methods</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Technical Approach</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frontend</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">React Native for cross-platform mobile app</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">React Native</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Expo</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">TypeScript</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Backend</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Node.js API with MongoDB for data storage</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Node.js</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Express</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">MongoDB</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Payments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Mobile Money integration for Ghana</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Mobile Money</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Paystack</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Netlify for web, Expo for mobile</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Netlify</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Expo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
      
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Features Built</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Subscription Management</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Users can subscribe to weekly boxes, choose sizes (Small, Standard, Family), and manage their subscriptions easily.
          </p>
          </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Swap System</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Customers can swap items they don't want for alternatives. Built with simple SMS integration for easy use.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Farmer Stories</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            QR codes on boxes link to stories about the farmers, their methods, and why they grow what they grow.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Pickup Points</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Strategic pickup locations in busy neighborhoods with QR code check-in system.
          </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Challenges & Learnings</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Logistics Complexity:</strong> Managing inventory, farmer coordination, and delivery schedules was more complex than expected.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>User Education:</strong> People needed to understand the subscription model and how the swap system worked.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Farmer Onboarding:</strong> Getting farmers comfortable with the technology and process took time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Key Learning:</strong> Building the technology was the easy part. The real challenge was building trust and changing behavior.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Current Status</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          MarketMate is currently in development. I've built the core features and am working on:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1 list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Finalizing the farmer onboarding process</li>
          <li>Testing the pickup point system</li>
          <li>Refining the user experience based on feedback</li>
          <li>Building partnerships with local farmers</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="/projects/marketmate" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80">View Project</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">All Projects</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">Ask Questions</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
</Layout>
<Footer />
